jsonBody.description:
Central Location in London’s West End

Z Covent Garden offers a 113 bedroom hotel in the heart of London’s West End. The property is conveniently situated just behind St Paul’s Church and Covent Garden’s famous Piazza, London’s first ever modern square.

Modern Amenities and Comfortable Rooms

Guests can enjoy complimentary Wi-Fi throughout the hotel, including the reception and cafe areas. All bedrooms are equipped with en-suite shower rooms and large Samsung HD TVs with full access to Sky and BT Sport channels.

Convenient Access to Popular Attractions

Located a short walk from Covent Garden's bars, restaurants, museums, galleries, and boutique shops, the hotel is perfect for guests wanting to explore London’s vibrant scene. With Covent Garden tube station a mere 350 meters away, and Leicester Square and Charing Cross stations within 500 meters, transportation is a breeze.

Book your stay at Z Covent Garden for a memorable experience in London’s bustling West End.

jsonBody.important_info:
Guests are required to show a photo identification and credit card upon check-in. Please note that all Special Requests are subject to availability and additional charges may apply.
In response to Coronavirus (COVID-19), additional safety and sanitation measures are in effect at this property.
Due to Coronavirus (COVID-19), this property is taking steps to help protect the safety of guests and staff. Certain services and amenities may be reduced or unavailable as a result.
In accordance with government guidelines to minimise transmission of the Coronavirus (COVID-19), this property currently isn't accepting guests from certain countries, during dates where such guidelines exist.
Please note that the card used to make your reservation has to be presented upon arrival along with a matching photo ID.

If the guest is using a corporate or third-party credit card, (Not traveling with the guest) an authorization form must be signed by the card holder, also a copy of the credit card and a Valid Government Issued ID must be provided.

Children (under the age of 18) can stay only if accompanied by a parent or a guardian.
